Caption:
Buckle up, because the future of mobility has arrived!

At the Bharat Mobility Global Expo, I had the thrill of exploring the bold and masculine Hyundai CRETA Electric—and it’s nothing short of revolutionary.

0-100 kmph in just 7.9 seconds—speed redefined.

473 km range on a single charge—long drives just got electric.

Next-level features like Active Air Flaps, In-Car Payments, and a battery heater for all-weather protection.

And here’s the kicker: the Find My Car feature with Surround View Monitoring. 

Ready to drive the change? Visit your nearest dealerships and explore how impressive Hyundai CRETA Electric is!

Caption:
Comment karo "Samsung" to get video on Galaxy Fit3 band 😉🚀 #ad

Samsung has launched their best mid range phone A55 5G📱to the meet the level of flagship under 40k budget only 😉

🚩 Samsung A55 5G comes with a 6.6-inch FHD+ resolution display with 120Hz refresh rate and an optical in-display fingerprint sensor, protected by Gorilla Glass Victus+. 

🚀 Galaxy A55 is powered by the Exynos 1480 SoC.

📸 The Galaxy A55 has a triple camera setup with a 50 MP primary sensor, a 12 MP ultra-wide angle lens, a 5 MP macro lens and a 32 MP selfie camera.

✅ In terms of features, these devices offer optical image stabilization (OIS) and video digital image stabilization (VDIS), Night Portrait mode, and enhanced Nightography features, powered by advanced AI Image Signal Processing (ISP).

🔋It offer a 5,000 mAh battery with support for 25W fast charging.
